### Get All Foods and Combos with Images and Promotions - Lấy tất cả Food và Combo kèm Image và Promotion
GET {{host}}/api/food/all-foods-and-combos
Content-Type: application/json

### Test with different endpoints for comparison

### Get Foods only (existing endpoint)
GET {{host}}/api/food
Content-Type: application/json

### Get Combos only (existing endpoint)  
GET {{host}}/api/combo/combos
Content-Type: application/json

### Variables
@host = https://localhost:7001